{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM05_ST4_010.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1a,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hey, Ayesha. So, you came back here?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I wanted to do some synthesis that<CR>I can only do at my workshop."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Oh, that's right! Ernie, I made some progress with Nio."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Really? Judging from the sound of it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x126,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "It should be a good story, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I still can't say, but I'm hoping to give it a happy ending."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x128,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I see. I can't really help,<CR>and all I can do is worry..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "But I'll always be rooting for you so I can hear how your story turns out."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I knew it! Nio's safe, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x123,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "So, the Nio I saw wasn't just an illusion, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Yes! We aren't able to physically reach her yet, but after a little more...I'm sure we will."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x126,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I see. I don't know all the details,<CR>but I'm sure you can do it, Ayesha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x127,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I may not be of much help, but let me know if there's anything I can do."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Ernie...thank you so much."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Oh, there's one thing I need to talk to you about. You know how the ground was rumbling a little while ago?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I think there are several places where the rumbling has caused roads to fall apart and damage to the ruins."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Slags from the ruins have been appearing frequently on roads where we usually don't see them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Ergh, th-that's... I'm sorry."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Why are you apologizing?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Well, I thought it might be my fault."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x5f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Haha, of course it's not. Anyway, I just wanted to let you know that it's dangerous, so be extra careful."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x61,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "This is just a hunch, but...I feel like something bad is gonna happen."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "My hunches prove to be right pretty often, so please be careful, Ayesha."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x1a0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Well, I've gotta get going now. See you!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Slags appearing on roads...<CR>It's probably because of the<CR>Flower Crystal..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I might've caused something terrible.<CR>I hope it hasn't caused anyone any trouble..."
        }
    ]
}